abstract:
We analyze confirmed cases and new hospitalizations in Wisconsin in the weeks surrounding the April 7, 2020 election, and find no evidence of a surge in SARS-CoV-2 transmission.
Competing Interest Statement

Funding Statement
author: Lawrence M Wein; Kathy Leung; Kuang Xu; Joseph T Wu
title: No Detectable Surge in SARS-CoV-2 Transmission due to the April 7, 2020 Wisconsin Election
